# UserController - Admin user management
# Requires admin Authorization header

### List users
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create user
POST {{base_url}}/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "0123456789"
}

### Get user
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Update user status
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/admin/users/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": 1
}

### Update user roles
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/admin/users/1/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "roles": ["admin"]
}

### Delete user
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
